data.description: Looking for quiet country living? Look no further! This property is part of a community lovingly known as Forest Glade. This home oozes small town charm, nestled right outside of the city limits. Built in 1966, this 3 bed 2 bath home sits on almost 3 acres, is cross-fenced, and is covered in producing pecan trees with a solitary pear tree. The house is move in ready, just waiting for you to add your own homey touches. Call and set up a showing today!
